  "text": "Our technique complements these strategies by focusing on the assessment of cognitive profiles, which would help obtain a set of well-defined requirements. For instance, starting from a goaloriented method [CITATION_1] , our technique introduced in (Martínez Carod and Cechich, 2007) extends goal graphs by using stakeholders' cognitive characteristics.",
